It's a pretty good movie if you're looking for smutty scenes I guess but Christian and Ana's relationship? Eh, it could use some work. I guess we'll just have to see how it progresses. text: Book I was a introduction to these characters! But as all the fan's know book 2 and 3 are by far the best! The love story really starts in book 2! You find out what Christian has experienced in his childhood and how he got to the world he's in with his adopted family, only knowing the world he was seduced into to by Ms Lincoln when he was a teen!  While Ana experiences alot of first with Christian, Christian in turn experiences some of his firsts with Ana! He may have exceeded in his business life, he's emotionally behind in his personal life! His childhood trama, experienced with his real Mom and her pimp stopped his emotional growth! That trama stayed with him, even as his new Mom and family who adopted him came into his life was loving and supportive of him! Ana was a unexpected surprise to Christian and that all changed when their relationship stopped! She opened up in him the possibility of more and that is where book 2 starts! Two people in love and finding a way to open up, be vulnerable and communicate with each other! I think alot of people relate to that!  The trailer looks fantastic, looks like their giving the fan's what they want and in the end, yes we're intrigued! Wonder what that next trailer will bring when it hits! I believe Darker will deliver on the sexy romance and as a thriller because that is what book 2 was, that's what really brought the fan's in, in the end it's at its heart a love story between Ana and Christian!
